data.description: Waterfront property on saltwater gulf access canal in Plantation Island!! Enjoy the beautiful waters of the Gulf of Mexico on your boat with your own ** PRIVATE DOCK ** and ** PRIVATE BOAT RAMP **. This 2 Bedroom/2 Bathroom elevated home sits on your very own Gulf access canal front lot!! Also, since the home was elevated, there was NO storm surge flood damage from Hurricane Ian inside the home. Perfect seasonal/vacation home or enjoy the fishing from your private dock year-round in this very friendly community! This is a Fisherman’s Delight. This property is located in the 10,000 Islands, home to the best and most incredible Florida saltwater fishing around. This is natural Florida at its finest. The home features a split floor plan, the bedrooms are on each side of the unit with the kitchen and family room in between. New wood laminate flooring installed at the end 2021/early 2022. Metal roof was installed in 2019. Fish house next to the dock makes an excellent fish station. Come and enjoy true Florida Living with your own dock, ramp and saltwater canal!
